BULLET::::- Associated Press. "&lt;a href="http%3A//wtop.com/%3Fnid%3D25%26amp%3Bsid%3D888012"&gt;Manhunt Shuts Down Virginia Tech&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AWTOP"&gt;WTOP&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, August 21, 2006

