BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/5275062.stm"&gt;Walesa leaves Solidarity movement&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABBC%20News%20Online"&gt;BBC News Online&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, August 22, 2006

</ul>
<ul>
BULLET::::- Monica Scislowska. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.cbsnews.com/stories/2006/08/22/ap/world/mainD8JLL3MO0.shtml"&gt;Poland's Walesa Quits Solidarity Union&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AAssociated%20Press"&gt;Associated Press&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, August 22, 2006

</ul>
