BULLET::::- Rathin Das. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.hindustantimes.com/news/181_1772777%2C000900040003.htm"&gt;Sweet water miracle in Gujarat too&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AHindustan%20Times"&gt;Hindustan Times&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, August 19, 2006
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//timesofindia.indiatimes.com/articleshow/1907898.cms"&gt;People taste "sweet" sea water in Mumbai&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Times%20of%20India"&gt;The Times of India&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, August 19, 2006
