BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.interfax.ru/e/B/politics/28.html%3Fmenu%3D1%26amp%3Bid_issue%3D11577223"&gt;Russia, Ukraine can achieve partnership through compromise - Putin&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AInterfax"&gt;Interfax&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, August 23, 2006

</ul>
<ul>
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.rferl.org/"&gt;Ukraine Marks National Independence Day&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ARadio%20Free%20Liberty"&gt;Radio Free Liberty&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, August 23, 2006

