BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/5281494.stm"&gt;Greenpeace 'siege' over in France&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABBC%20News%20Online"&gt;BBC News Online&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, August 24, 2006

</ul>
<ul>
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.lemonde.fr/web/article/0%2C1-0%25402-3228%2C36-805567%254051-805163%2C0.html"&gt;Le "Rainbow-Warrior II" se dirige vers l'Espagne, la préfecture maritime va saisir le parquet&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ALe%20Monde"&gt;Le Monde&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, August 24, 2006 &lt;big&gt;&lt;span style="color:red;"&gt;«[ create French language template]»&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/big&gt;

</ul>
