BULLET::::- Bruce Campion-Smith. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.thestar.com/NASApp/cs/ContentServer%3Fpagename%3Dthestar/Layout/Article_Type1%26amp%3Bc%3DArticle%26amp%3Bcid%3D1156369812500%26amp%3Bcall_pageid%3D968332188854%26amp%3Bcol%3D968350060724"&gt;Afghans vent anger at Canadians&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AToronto%20Star"&gt;Toronto Star&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, August 24, 2006

