BULLET::::- Associated Press. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.easybourse.com/Website/dynamic/News.php%3FNewsID%3D46571%26amp%3Blang%3Dfra%26amp%3BNewsRubrique%3D2"&gt;Nigerian Army Burn Houses After Soldier Killed -Witnesses&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AEasybourse"&gt;Easybourse&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, August 25, 2006

