BULLET::::- Saleem Shahid. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.dawn.com/2006/08/27/top1.htm"&gt;Bugti killed in operation: Six officers among 21 security personnel dead&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ADawn"&gt;Dawn&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, August 26, 2006

