BULLET::::- ShadowMonkey. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.shadowmonkey.net/articles/general/just-say-no-to-just-say-no.html"&gt;Just Say No to 'Just Say No'&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3Ashadowmonkey.net"&gt;shadowmonkey.net&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, August 29, 2006

</ul>
