<ul>
BULLET::::- NASA. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.prnewswire.com/cgi-bin/stories.pl%3FACCT%3D104%26amp%3BSTORY%3D/www/story/08-30-2006/0004424282%26amp%3BEDATE%3D"&gt;Caught in the Act, Scientists Watch Supernova Explode&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3APR%20Newswire"&gt;PR Newswire&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, August 30, 2006

</ul>
