BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.cnn.com/2006/HEALTH/08/31/cnna.rosenberg/index.html"&gt;Cancer researcher: 'This is just a start'&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ACNN.com"&gt;CNN.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, August 31, 2006
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.cnn.com/2006/HEALTH/08/31/cancer.vaccine/index.html"&gt;Therapy turns patients' cells into cancer smart bombs&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ACNN.com"&gt;CNN.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, August 31, 2006
