BULLET::::- George Stephanopoulos. "&lt;a href="http%3A//abcnews.go.com/Politics/story%3Fid%3D2375968"&gt;So Now We Know: It's True: The Cover-Up Is Worse than the Crime&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AABC%20News"&gt;ABC News&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, August 30, 2006

