BULLET::::- Robert Levine of The New York Times. "&lt;a href="http%3A//thechronicleherald.ca/Business/526289.html"&gt;Can MySpace take a bite out of Apple?&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AHalifax%20Chronicle-Herald"&gt;Halifax Chronicle-Herald&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, September 7, 2005

</ul>
