BULLET::::- Howard Kurtz. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.msnbc.msn.com/id/14707869/"&gt;Clinton officials rip ABC's 'The Path to 9/11'&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Washington%20Post"&gt;The Washington Post&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, September 8, 2006
