BULLET::::- Sarah Boseley. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.guardian.co.uk/food/Story/0%2C%2C1865786%2C00.html"&gt;Junk food makers using internet to target children, says watchdog&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Guardian"&gt;The Guardian&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, September 6, 2006

</ul>
